review_blob: Craziness, coffee to chocolate to chile and back again.  Rich and creamy with a big foamy head in my snifta.  You either love it or hate it and this guy loved it.
beer_name: Odd Side Ales Mayan Mocha  Stout

review_blob: Super clear for a wheat but the hops come shining (literally) through with clean clear citrus bitterness and a focused finish.  Everything that Bells Solsun once was and what Oberon will never be.  Bazinga!
